{"tid":1355560,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"興華邨女子墮樓亡","createTime":"2019-07-23T10:30:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T10:34:17.000Z","uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4b45039fec78821546ff5027552f1cdd2cbe8b12","tid":1355560,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T10:30:34.000Z","msg":"柴灣有人從高處墮下，今早(23日)11時許，一名女子自興華(二)邨裕興樓高處墮下，倒臥對開山坡，有住戶乍聞巨響，循聲查看揭發，慌忙報警。救護員到場，經檢驗後證實女子當場死亡。<br />\n<br />\n警方其後證實女事主姓冼(47歲)，初步調查後，相信她從上址天台墮下，事件並無可疑。警員在場並無檢獲遺書，案列自殺處理。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190723/photo/bkn-20190723122533209-0723_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190723170134\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190723%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190723122533209-0723_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190723170134&h=cd13c75e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190723/photo/bkn-20190723122533209-0723_00822_001_02p.jpg?20190723170134\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190723%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190723122533209-0723_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20190723170134&h=950d6e76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n防止自殺求助熱線：<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會： 2389 2222<br />\n生命熱線： 2382 0000<br />\n明愛向晴軒： 18288<br />\n社會福利署： 2343 2255<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)： 2896 0000<br />\n東華三院芷若園： 18281<br />\n醫管局精神健康專線： 2466 7350<br />\n利民會： 3512 2626<br />\n賽馬會青少年情緒健康網上支援平台「Open噏」：<a href=\"http://www.openup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.openup.hk&d=DQhhZyJ%2BQntsVA7gHYVTWC8EbckYnMoWLUJTUpLSOd8%3D&h=285dce37\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.openup.hk</a>"},{"pid":"0cbbae29117eedd772ccba9f40e5ef7611fe8a52","tid":1355560,"uid":239663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T10:34:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5292b94694081b9efef5389212a9ed5fb7029cfb","tid":1355560,"uid":256274,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"